<p><b>Truffle Oil</b> is an <a href="/Artisan_Goods" title="Artisan Goods">Artisan Good</a> made in the <a href="/Oil_Maker" title="Oil Maker">Oil Maker</a> from a <a href="/Truffle" title="Truffle">Truffle</a>. It takes 6 hours to produce. Despite being listed as "A gourmet cooking ingredient" there are no cooking recipes that use it, but it is used to make the <a href="/Rain_Totem" title="Rain Totem">Rain Totem</a>.
</p>
