<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Bundles">Bundles</span></h2>
<p>Truffle Oil is an option for the <span style="display:inline; margin-right:0;"><img alt="Bundle Purple.png" src="/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/24px-Bundle_Purple.png" decoding="async" width="24" height="24" srcset="/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/36px-Bundle_Purple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png 2x" /> <a href="/Bundles#Artisan_Bundle" title="Bundles">Artisan Bundle</a> in the <a href="/Bundles#Pantry" title="Bundles">Pantry</a></span>.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Crafting">Crafting</span></h2>
<p>Truffle Oil is used to make the following items:
</p>
