<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Tailoring">Tailoring</span></h2>
<p>Truffle Oil can be used in the spool of the <a href="/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine" title="2 Willow Lane">Sewing Machine</a> to create the dyeable <a href="/Tailoring" title="Tailoring">Dark Bandana Shirt</a>.  <a href="/File:Shirt262a.png" class="image"><img alt="Shirt262a.png" src="/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/85/Shirt262a.png/24px-Shirt262a.png" decoding="async" width="24" height="24" srcset="/mediawiki/images/8/85/Shirt262a.png 1.5x" /></a> It can be used in <a href="/Dyeing" title="Dyeing">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href="/Emily" title="Emily">Emily</a>'s and <a href="/Haley" title="Haley">Haley</a>'s house, <a href="/2_Willow_Lane" title="2 Willow Lane">2 Willow Lane</a>.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Quests">Quests</span></h2>
<ul><li>Mayor <a href="/Lewis" title="Lewis">Lewis</a> requests Truffle Oil by mail on the 21st of <a href="/Summer" title="Summer">Summer</a> (year 2) in the <a href="/Quests#Mayor.27s_Need" title="Quests">"Mayor's Need" Quest</a>.  The reward is <span style="display: none;">data-sort-value="750"&gt;</span><span class="no-wrap"><img alt="Gold.png" src="/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" srcset="/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x" />750g</span> and 1 <a href="/Friendship" title="Friendship">Friendship</a> heart.<br />Note that Lewis will send the letter triggering the quest regardless of whether or not the player owns a <a href="/Pig" title="Pig">pig</a>.</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="History">History</span></h2>
<ul><li><a href="/Version_History#1.0" title="Version History">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>
<li><a href="/Version_History#1.4" title="Version History">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href="/Tailoring" title="Tailoring">Tailoring</a>.</li></ul>
